attachments.title: Imminent Google Nexus 2016 Release as Epic Price Cuts Leave Nexus 5X Down to $285, Nexus 6P to $399
attachments.text: Both the Nexus 5X and 6P have become more affordable than ever, selling for dirt cheap price of just $285 a pop that makes the Pure Android flagships of 2015 hard to resist. But even more tantalizing is the thought that with the Nexus deals galore, release date of the refresh, the Nexus 2016 series, looms large on the horizon.
